================================================================================
Upstream specifications
================================================================================

This library targets the Exploit Prediction Scoring System (EPSS) published by
the Forum of Incident Response and Security Teams (FIRST):

  - Overview:          https://www.first.org/epss/
  - REST API:          https://www.first.org/epss/api
  - Daily score feed:  https://epss.cyentia.com/

The EPSS scores themselves are produced by the EPSS Special Interest Group and
distributed under the terms documented on the FIRST EPSS site. This library
contains no EPSS data — it only fetches and parses it.
